      <title>美银表示，美联储降息一年后，现金抢购潮将出现逆转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/rush-to-cash-will-reverse-a-year-after-fed-cuts-start-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者仍在涌向现金基金，美国银行策略师表示，历史表明，赎回要到美联储开始降息一年后才会开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/rush-to-cash-will-reverse-a-year-after-fed-cuts-start-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 08:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
